      "status": "rejected_for_now",
      "reason": "Adding a leading PHP namespace slash to @:native still does not create an owned receiver-less global function call representation."
    },
    {
      "id": "php-syntax-code",
      "status": "rejected",
      "reason": "Raw php.Syntax.code would paste target PHP into Haxe strings and bypass typed Haxe ownership. It may only appear in a narrow documented boundary, not as the selected porting strategy."
